CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1963, pg. 19, reads: "1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama Exhibitors who were not shown on last week's picture page are shown here... 8. Breakfast Cheer Coffee: Marquita Harris and Chuck Cox... All Home-A-Rama Photos (Including last week's) by Charles (Teenie) Harris."
TitMainTitle: Marquita Harris passing out sample of coffee to man, with Chuck Cox standing beside her in Breakfast Cheer Coffee booth, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
